---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title="First Glance - 专注新标签页">
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="text-center mb-20">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-6">First Glance</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-[#6b4f4f] mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        将新标签页变成专注仪表盘，一眼看到今日最重要的任务。与滴答清单无缝同步。
      </p>
      <a
        href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore"
        class="inline-block bg-[#4f2b2b] text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-lg font-medium hover:bg-[#3a1f1f] transition-colors"
      >
        安装 Chrome 扩展
      </a>
    </section>

    <!-- Features -->
    <section class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-20">
      <div class="bg-white/50 rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">聚焦视图</h3>
        <p class="text-[#6b4f4f]">自动展示今日最高优先级任务，保持专注。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white/50 rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">快速操作</h3>
        <p class="text-[#6b4f4f]">直接在新标签页完成、编辑或创建任务。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white/50 rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">多种主题</h3>
        <p class="text-[#6b4f4f]">支持多种配色风格，适配你的审美。</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="text-center text-[#8b7355]">
      <p>&copy; 2026 First Glance</p>
    </footer>
  </main>
</Layout>
